Based on the Insight Toolkit ITK, RTK provides: basic operators for reconstruction (e.g. filtering, forward, projection and backprojection), multithreaded CPU and GPU versions, tools for respiratory motion correction, I/O for several scanners, preprocessing of raw data for scatter correction.


